   Mary T. Handley, 61, of Bay City, Mich., planned to vacation in
New Zealand before a convention of the Dale Carnegie Systems, said
her husband, John Desso.
   She owned Handley and Associates Inc., which offered the Dale
Carnegie motivational course. She had six grown children.
