pleasure trip to New Zealand, Australia, and the Philippines, said
her cousin, Ina Martin of Conway, Ark.
   Miss Harley, a native of Paris, Ark., was founder of Rose Harley
Institute in Hackensack, which sponsored the Dale Carnegie
motivational courses in northern New Jersey.
